# Routes

### Marketing & Communication

 * `/`                              
 * `/pricing`                       API Integration
 * `/contact`                       The RequestForm
 * `/servers/:server_id/ssh`        SSH RequestForm
 * `/servers/:server_id/dns/custom` DNS RequestForm

### Servers
 * `/`                              serverController.listServers
 * `/server/:id`                    serverController.getServer

### Hardware

 * `/server/:id/powercycle`         doManageServer.dropletPowerCycle
 * `/server/:id/poweron`            doManageServer.dropletPowerOn
 * `/server/:id/poweroff`           doManageServer.dropletPowerOff
 * `/server/:id/destroy`            doManageServer.dropletDestroy
 * `/server/:id/shutdown`           @todomabey SoftwareRestart
 * `/server/:id/restart`            @todomabey GracefulPowerdown

### Snapshots

 * `/server/boot`                   doMakeServer.postMakeServer
 * `/server/:id/snapshots`          doManageServer.viewServersSnapshots
 * `/server/:id/snapshots/:slot`    doManageServer.viewSnapshot
 * `/server/:id/snapshots/make`     doManageServer.makeSnapshot
 * `/server/:id/snapshots/delete`   doManageServer.destroySnapshot
 * `/server/:id/rebuild`            doManageServer.selectSnapshot

### DNS

 * `/servers/:server_id/dns`        Subdomain DNS Management
 * `/servers/:server_id/dns/add`    Add A Record
 * `/servers/:server_id/dns/remove` Remove A Record

### Script Manager

 * `/server/:id/runscript`          scriptController.postScript

  Module/Plugin Format
  `ls -la`
  `website start`




### StarBound Specific

 * `/server/:id/:slug`                   setPasswordForm
 * `/server/:id/:slug/worlds`            sbWorldManager.viewWorlds
 * `/server/:id/:slug/worlds/save`       sbWorldManager.saveWorld
 * `/server/:id/:slug/players`           sbPlayerManager.viewPlayers
 * `/server/:id/:slug/players/profile`   sbPlayerManager.editPlayerProfile

StarryPy, StarryBound Manager

### Node Application Server

 * `/server/:id/:slug/node`              Restart,View Data,Edit Secrets?


